Milpitas.Mabury: Mabury (pronounced "may-berry") is an area in San Jose, California belonging to the zip code of 95133. There are two parks belonging to the area of Mabury. One, Overfelt Gardens (37.363029°N 121.853528°W﻿ / 37.363029; -121.853528), located at McKee Road and Educational Park Drive between East San Jose and the North Valley, pays tributes to Asian culture that thrives in and around its parts.
